  <brief_title>Randomized Trial on Scarpa Fascia Preservation During Hernio-abdominoplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Scarpa Fascia Preservation Versus Removal During Hernio-abdominoplasty: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
