  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomized trial aimed to assess the efficacy of preservation of Scarpa's fascia during
      hernio-abdominoplasty in reducing the volume of postoperative drainage, accelerating time to
      drain removal and recovery, and reducing complication rate.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
